BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 697.48 Td (Panel Subtitle: Quick answers to common questions) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 666.96 Td (1. What services does your company provide?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 648.44 Td (We provide website development, custom software development, eCommerce solutions, mobile) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 633.92 Td (applications, UI/UX design, cloud solutions, API integration, ERP/CRM systems, and ongoing) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 619.40 Td (maintenance and support.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 592.88 Td (2. How much does a typical project cost?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 574.36 Td (It depends on scope - a marketing website and a custom ERP system are very different builds.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 559.84 Td (We give a clear, itemized quote after understanding your requirements during the discovery call,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 545.32 Td (so you know the cost before any work starts, not after.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 518.80 Td (3. How long does a project usually take?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 500.28 Td (A standard business website typically takes a few weeks, while custom software or eCommerce) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 485.76 Td (platforms can take a couple of months depending on complexity. We share a realistic timeline) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 471.24 Td (during planning, before any commitment is made.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 444.72 Td (4. Do you work with startups, or only established businesses?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 426.20 Td (Both. We work with early-stage founders building their first product as well as established) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 411.68 Td (companies modernizing existing systems - the process adjusts to where you're starting from.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 385.16 Td (5. What does your development process look like?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 366.64 Td (We move through four stages: discovery and consultation, design and planning, development) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 352.12 Td (and engineering, and launch and beyond. You get visibility at every stage, not just a final reveal) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 337.60 Td (at the end.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 311.08 Td (6. Do you provide support after the project launches?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 292.56 Td (Yes. Launch is not where we stop - we offer ongoing maintenance, security updates, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 278.04 Td (feature support so your product keeps working as your business grows.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 251.52 Td (7. Can you work with our existing team or systems?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 233.00 Td (Yes, we regularly integrate with in-house teams, existing codebases, and third-party tools rather) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 218.48 Td (than insisting on starting from zero. We will tell you honestly if a full rebuild is the better option,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 203.96 Td (but we don't default to it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 177.44 Td (8. What technologies do you use?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 158.92 Td (We choose the right stack for the project rather than forcing every client into the same tools.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 144.40 Td (This typically means modern frameworks for web and mobile, cloud platforms for hosting and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 129.88 Td (scaling, and proven, well-supported technology over anything experimental.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 103.36 Td (9. What's the first step to getting started?) Tj ET
endstream
